data.description: *INVESTORS & CASH BUYERS TAKE NOTICE* Multi-family home with lots of potential. Property needs work, likely won't qualify for traditional financing. Option to heat home with oil or natural gas. House comes equipped with both options. This home is located on a dead end street and offers some off-street parking. Walkout basement leads you to a good-sized backyard with water views of the French River. First floor unit is spacious with an office nook, living room, good sized kitchen, full bath, and two bedrooms. Second floor unit is more updated with three bedrooms, a living room, full bath, and open kitchen. Third floor unit has 2 bedrooms, open kitchen, full bathroom, and living room.  Again, this property needs some love but amazing upside and potential!  Do not walk the property without a scheduled showing. Reach out today!  Great money maker once updated!
